Dear Google Team, the image of penne  
bolognese (meat sauce), the second from top on the infringing site is mine
 
and belongs to my recipe site finestchef.com. Please replace it with the  
original page on your Image Search if at all possible. I have personally  
cooked this pasta and photographed it to illustrate my recipe. Thank you  
for your assistance. Best regards.
